1. *Rad* je najvažniji deo života. (Work is the most important part of life.)
2. On je *radio* celu noć. (He was working all night.)
3. Ona voli da *radi*. (She likes to work.)
4. Naš *rad* je završen. (Our work is finished.)
5. *Radili* smo do kasno u noć. (We worked until late at night.)
6. Šta *radiš*? (What are you doing?)
7. Ona je *radila* u banki. (She was working in a bank.)
8. Oni su *radili* zajedno. (They were working together.)